Seventh ACCAT Workshop
on Applied and Computational
Category Theory (ACCAT 2012)

Tallinn, Estonia
Sun, April 01, 2012

(co-located with ETAPS 2012)

http://www.cosy.sbg.ac.at/~tsoboll/ACCAT
=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=
